episodes.title: Without Further Ado
episodes.plot: Jonathan returns to his hometown to make over his high school music teacher, a selfless educator whose fiery red mullet hasn't changed in 30 years.

episodes.title: Disabled but Not Really
episodes.plot: A former bad boy who turned his life around after becoming paralyzed gets a wheelchair-accessible home and a new image to match his positive outlook.

episodes.title: Stoner Skates By
episodes.plot: His 10-year-old daughter calls him a "man child." But can this larger-than-life single dad grow up and become the adult she needs him to be?

episodes.title: How Wanda Got Her Groove Back
episodes.plot: A demanding drill-team leader who's set in her ways learns to shed her tough skin, soften her style -- and open up to her two grown daughters.

episodes.title: On Golden Kenny
episodes.plot: The Fab Five help a kind but lonely bachelor find unconditional love and get his dusty home ready for visitors, the first guests he's had in years.

episodes.title: A Tale of Two Cultures
episodes.plot: A proud Chicana woman and arts advocate trades her dated locks for a polished look that gives her the confidence to talk publicly about her passions.

episodes.title: Soldier Returns Home
episodes.plot: A scruffy ex-soldier who builds houses for homeless veterans spruces up to reconnect with his wife and finds unexpected strength in vulnerability.

episodes.title: Farm to Able
episodes.plot: A recently divorced farmer who's weathered hard times makes room for self-care and turns his barn into a chic farm-to-table dining space.
